story_teamflare_02_10000/2401_1001_0200_: Yup, I’m fine! We’re all fine!
story_teamflare_02_10000/2401_1001_0300_: But if this keeps on much longer...
story_teamflare_02_10000/2401_1001_0400_: Ahaha... Looks like we’re coming to the end?
story_teamflare_02_10000/2401_1001_0700_:
I’ll draw Team Rocket’s attention and deal with
their attacks!
story_teamflare_02_10000/2401_1001_0800_: You and Mimi can use that opportunity to escape!
story_teamflare_02_10000/2401_1001_0900_:
What are you saying, Mr. Looker? I don’t wanna

story_teamflare_02_10000/2401_1001_1000_:

story_teamflare_02_10000/2401_1001_1200_: Are you done with the chitchat?
story_teamflare_02_10000/2401_1001_1300_:

story_teamflare_02_10000/2401_1001_1800_:
My name is Anabel. I’m the head of a secret
division of the International Police.
story_teamflare_02_10000/2401_1001_2300_: That’s right, Emma. She’s my superior!
story_teamflare_02_10000/2401_1001_2400_: So she’s basically a big shot!
story_teamflare_02_10000/2401_1001_2500_: Wow! I see! You must be cool!
story_teamflare_02_10000/2401_1001_2700_:
Yes, I know. I’ve already been informed of
her identity.
story_teamflare_02_10000/2401_1001_3000_:
Thank you for cooperating with Mr. Looker during
his investigation.
story_teamflare_02_10000/2401_1001_3100_: Let me join you both from here!
story_teamflare_02_10000/2401_1001_3200_: Sure thing! Nice to meet you, Chief! ♪
story_teamflare_02_10000/2401_1001_3300_: Now, both of you! Are you ready to fight back?
story_teamflare_02_10000/2401_1001_3500_:
Since I’m here now, I won’t let either of you
get hurt!
story_teamflare_02_10000/2401_1001_3700_: Your teamwork with Snorlax is awesome, too!
story_teamflare_02_10000/2401_1001_3800_: Heh... You two are so reliable!
story_teamflare_02_10000/2401_1001_3900_:
Ugh... We didn’t expect to have to battle an extra

story_teamflare_02_10000/2401_1001_4000_: Looker! Emma! Are you both OK?
story_teamflare_02_10000/2401_1001_4200_:
Let’s talk later! Now’s the time to battle
Team Rocket!
